TopicTitle: I got no missions on new career

Articles.Content:
As the title says.. I have just started a new career with the mods listed in the image and I am not having any missions at start. I did my first launch and now all I am getting is the "Test this part" missions, but no missions like "escape the atmosphere", or "get into orbit"...
